"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.3.1.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.3.1.2</span> Dragnet, seine</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">References:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">חֵרֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(cherem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:5\">EZK 26:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:14\">EZK 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:3\">EZK 32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:10\">EZK 47:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15\">HAB 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:16\">HAB 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:17\">HAB 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">σαγήνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(sagēnē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47\">MAT 13:47</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">Description:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0335_drag_net.png\" alt=\"Men drawing in a dragnet\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">Men drawing in a dragnet (George Louis Faber, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>The dragnet was a long net hanging vertically in the water with floats at the upper edge and weights at the lower edge.</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">Usage:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>The dragnet was drawn in by men working in boats or from shore. As the ends were drawn together to the boat or drawn ashore, fish were trapped in the area enclosed by the net.</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">Translation:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>A generic term for “net” may be used in languages that do not require that a distinction be made.</p>\n<p>In <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47\">MAT 13:47</a> the actual form of the net is not so important. What is significant is that the net was sufficiently large to catch a large number of different kinds of fish.</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15\">HAB 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:16\">HAB 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:17\">HAB 1:17</a>: See the comments at <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.3.1.1 Casting net&lt;REALIA:1.3.1.1&gt;</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
